metadata.description:
<< 1 >>

Slowly, she is fading. Her skin is slowly digested by sparkling crystals. 
...
The human world was finally conquered by AI spirits, whom main purpose was to idealise human nature.  

#6 was once a girl who love butterflies, has brought the beautiful creatures with her. Crystallised Butterflies stops themselves on her face forcing the crystals not to digest all of her, so she can retain part of her human nature. 
...
